-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="831bc549-ff76-45a6-a5a6-3e7ede8f12f5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rafj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-13vs0us"><div data-rid="c97e6da2-ce43-447d-8a38-3292d0b29f49" class="r-qak3yf alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Will it arrive in time for Father's Day?</p></span></div><div data-rid="7a94241c-026d-4de4-aea0-b9831c929ded" class="r-11bcw9x" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-go3nei" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rafj2:"><div data-rid="37f0246d-3b7e-48e1-9139-77e68bc30c7b" class="r-1uqpcm2"><div data-rid="90c8176f-31cb-4896-bc5d-c98890cb4213" class="r-1edtumg alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Yes. Orders usually ship within 1 to 2 business days, and most arrive within a week. Order by June 17th to guarantee delivery before Father's Day.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="cf9211a5-4a83-4efd-a376-dfbf3e5572f3" class="r-1bczhrn" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="498e2967-159a-4556-88eb-4a27d5cb983e" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Refj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-n0a37p"><div data-rid="784af152-d9d9-4cb7-8b7b-e28e49b7f530" class="r-ozy51w alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Can I return if he already owns one?</p></span></div><div data-rid="f58d92d7-aea4-42aa-8770-afbf09af21d5" class="r-zo7zpo" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-126h4tj" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Refj2:"><div data-rid="cabd8644-5bf4-4e55-aa60-d6140cd85d3a" class="r-1tbsolk"><div data-rid="9c77edd9-b1e7-4256-962c-ff7b48646542" class="r-w1ro6n alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>It happens. If he already has the product you picked, we'll exchange it for something else in our lineup, or refund you within 30 days. Just reach out to our team and we'll handle it.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="d9ece2cd-96d3-4b56-8745-f552596152c5" class="r-1nlkcaz" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="9472ea79-ce07-484b-9947-6830c7173eeb" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rifj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-dzfnv5"><div data-rid="961a91ee-07f6-41da-86e3-e61fde9ea486" class="r-crqdl1 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Does he need a smartphone?</p></span></div><div data-rid="bc0702fb-0b5f-4f3f-8ce7-4047225d18de" class="r-gn3qs2" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-oy6pdt" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rifj2:"><div data-rid="c3e2ff0e-86f2-424f-87ba-ecc48fc28fe7" class="r-wws3xf"><div data-rid="398c0765-efa3-4fab-b457-f34d4dbd3d0a" class="r-fxzv3g alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>He'll need a smartphone to set up his account and see his stats. The Smart Laser works on iPhone and Android. Arccos Air and Smart Sensors work best on iPhone (Android support is rolling out).</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="fedbe2f6-e331-415a-a691-bafb8e2e0fd8" class="r-36kk5p" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="a0e55ee4-914e-4e49-afb4-6548894aae60" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rmfj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-148qj9m"><div data-rid="997fa2d7-9a0b-4830-8708-216eec7cb24b" class="r-16s118h alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Is there a subscription?</p></span></div><div data-rid="73c17de8-947b-406e-baba-a1b0f61da071" class="r-8chryi" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1e3ul2t" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rmfj2:"><div data-rid="74fb4c32-1027-4e91-b270-a03f0ba61874" class="r-2rfkb2"><div data-rid="c8e6a0ec-e6a9-4d79-9bbd-65e7f1b3e6a2" class="r-1qfqnpu alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Yes, and here's the honest version: every Arccos product comes with a full year of membership included, free. After that first year, the membership renews so the app keeps getting smarter. Most golfers see real improvement long before year one is up.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="6f63ca35-ce28-43ce-a040-8e8ce240411d" class="r-1phyltz" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="7458b06f-8b9d-4a75-81bb-8d61736fbae1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rqfj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-tb65fh"><div data-rid="a1c5df2f-8995-45d0-817c-eab81cee3a8f" class="r-1kkyfoq alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>How do I give it as a gift?</p></span></div><div data-rid="6ba1dcfa-0389-4eaf-b358-f663bb532b0c" class="r-95ih2l" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-2gpzcw" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rqfj2:"><div data-rid="f9174d37-42df-4b9e-8e4d-491d5e6b1438" class="r-owkmzr"><div data-rid="1e0083bc-55e0-4d44-84c5-6109da0a67e1" class="r-1quch7d alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Order it to your address (not his) so the surprise stays intact. Once he opens it, he'll set up his own account in a few minutes, and the included one-year membership starts when he activates it, not when you order.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="bec13453-49b5-43a0-9b2c-71b3aa89cc87" class="r-1tmgvv4" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="d1339f70-b003-4e89-a57a-16a70c97dd3a" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rufj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-4pzw8"><div data-rid="22d6fbcb-c638-4ca5-aecf-d97a1e88cfa1" class="r-131lb0r alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>What's actually in the box?</p></span></div><div data-rid="32dea44e-a8fc-422a-a2e3-9720f57725cb" class="r-1t8k6ff" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1yrignn" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rufj2:"><div data-rid="1a473f9d-af81-494c-951e-eec86d6bfe1d" class="r-1g8ztlp